name: Jihosoft iPhone Backup Extractor Free
short_description:
Accidentally deleted something important on your iPhone? Lost or broken your iPhone? Use Jihosoft iPhone Backup Extractor Free to extract and retrieve data from iTunes backup, including photos, videos, messages, contacts, call logs, notes, WhatsApp, and so forth. It is helpful when you lost iPhone data due to failed iOS upgrade or sync, jailbreak, factory settings restore, ROM Flashing, virus attack, etc. 

The iPhone Backup Extractor can access any iTunes backup file created for all iPhone models, including iPhone 6, iPhone 6 Plus, iPhone 5S, iPhone 5, iPhone 4S, iPhone 4, and iPhone 3GS. It works well with all iOS including iOS 8. 

Key Features 
- Preview and check photos, videos, contacts, messages and other data previously before extraction and recovery. 
- Simple and wizard-like interface allows fast data extraction within a few simple clicks. 
- Completely free for personal and non-commercial use, no spyware, malware, or adware.
summary: Free Tool to Extract and Recover iPhone Data from iTunes Backup
